OS Assignment #3 v1.0

This is a program that solve thread synchronization problem with semaphore

This is run at ubuntu linux.

dining.c
	This is source file for dining philosoper problem.
	In here, we solve this problem with try_wait function that will implemented in sem.c

sem.c
	This is source of semaphore.
	Wait(), Siagnal() function is implemented.

sem.h
	This is source of semaphore structure.

test.c
	This is source of test file of multi thread.
	It shows multiple thread run concurrently

MakeFile
	A file that help control program files.
	With make statement, it supprot compile ,remove, execute program in easy way
	For example, make test(compile & execute program), make clean(removea all compiled file)
